{"tid":2179303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[是否自願]普及社區檢測計劃截至中午有逾11萬人預約登記","createTime":"2020-08-29T04:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T05:47:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b93456304cca0036310aa07a95cffec02ee88bbd","tid":2179303,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546654-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546654-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=13c5c92a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546654-20200829.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b011deb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546654-20200829.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n普及社區檢測計劃9月1日展開，市民今早7時開始可以上網預約。政府表示，截至中午12時，有大約11萬7700人透過上網預約登記。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者今早約9時到網站預約，過程大致順暢。申請人需要先填寫香港身份證或者出生證明書資料，然後需要同意《收集個人資料聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n《聲明》內容提及政府會根據檢測結果，使用收集到的個人資料與登記人跟進，所有個人資料不會向檢測機構披露，除測試結果屬陽性的個案需要另行跟進之外，其他個案的個人資料將保留至計劃完結後30日，其後將會銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n申請人其後需要輸入姓名、可接收短訊通知的電話號碼、揀選社區檢測中心、以及檢測日期和時段，確認資料無錯後，手機會收到確認短訊，整個過程大約2分鐘完成。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登記完有幾多人真係去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47d4b55a604a8fa3e395b73f9d46cfe245dab0b","tid":2179303,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"沉默的大多數繼續沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c4ae4ec1d33ce4c4933952c8cb18d69e1ef6da","tid":2179303,"uid":295855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"有689萬人唔支持喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac4708c524a77b0261ed1e296b9b2df4884d41e","tid":2179303,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">11萬支那港豬</span>"},{"pid":"e858737f82b0b32554b92a7de0cba1ab28c27618","tid":2179303,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"有身分證號碼就可以填 任篤"},{"pid":"a315882701dc121c7ac098a426cce053d8165d95","tid":2179303,"uid":226156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"屌，果500萬沉默大多數得11萬出黎，搞撚錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df85d3652b567ae29d0cd722740ffbdb52063f9","tid":2179303,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e858737f82b0b32554b92a7de0cba1ab28c27618","tid":2179303,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"有身分證號碼就可以填 任篤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"可重複登記？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a756daeb1a47f1f7fbce2db3a6172980698b0d2","tid":2179303,"uid":277659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"有冇得比較返派一萬頭幾個鐘登記數字"},{"pid":"8830e5b8aa53590f9f26aea7817e18bdee6935d5","tid":2179303,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"預左頭幾日點都多<br />\n否則太樣衰落大陸面"},{"pid":"c8064d3688614dfa07bb461f88d624c14021d0a1","tid":2179303,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"幾時先夠100萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314d379e3c63a50d75ab26028ff1c560cdd08645","tid":2179303,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike"